Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:03.23,Style1,,0,0,0,,St. Lobelia Academy, high school\N2nd-Year, Amakusa Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:04.83,jp.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,セントロベリア女学院高等部二年　天草紅緒
