Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:05.23,Style1,,0,0,0,,NSt. Lobelia Academy, high school\N2nd-Year, Amakusa Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:07.56,Style1,,0,0,0,,{/fnArial}♪{/r} {\i1}Lobelia{\i0} {/fnArial}♪{/r}
